{"tid":2493343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[共狗笠水科興當誅]中國計劃在7月前批准首款外國新冠疫苗","createTime":"2021-04-17T22:23:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T05:34:28.000Z","uid":26770,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a263a95c1a694be6ee351624d1b87ea7a2245ca6","tid":2493343,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T22:23:08.000Z","msg":"中國計劃在7月前批准首款外國新冠疫苗<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.wsj.com/articles/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E5%9C%A87%E6%9C%88%E5%89%8D%E6%89%B9%E5%87%86%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%BE%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97-11618621214\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.wsj.com%2Farticles%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583%25E5%259C%25A87%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2589%258D%25E6%2589%25B9%25E5%2587%2586%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%258B%2597-11618621214&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RPsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=5828ac92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cn.wsj.com/articles/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E5%9C%A87%E6%9C%88%E5%89%8D%E6%89%B9%E5%87%86%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%BE%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97-11618621214</a><br />\n據知情人士透露，中國官員一直在仔細審視<span class=\"xx-large\">BioNTech</span>新冠疫苗的臨床試驗數據，目前國內科學家和外國商界要求中國將其疫苗名冊擴大到國產疫苗之外的壓力越來越大。<br />\nKeith Zhai / Liza Lin / Sha Hua<br />\n2021年4月17日11:20 CST 更新<br />\n<br />\n據知情人士透露，中國計劃在7月前批准首款外國新冠疫苗，目前國內科學家和外國商界要求中國將其疫苗名冊擴大到國產疫苗之外的壓力越來越大。<br />\n<br />\n知情人士透露，中國官員一直在仔細審視德國BioNTech SE (BNTX)公司生產的新冠疫苗的臨床試驗數據，預計將在未來10周內為該疫苗的國內銷售開綠燈。一些人是在與政府官員和衛生官員的私下討論中被告知這一時間表的。其他人是聽取了內部討論簡報的政府官員。<br />\n<br />\nBioNTech去年12月同意與上海復星醫藥（集團）股份有限公司(Shanghai Fosun Pharmaceutical Group Co.)合作，在2021年向中國提供1億劑疫苗，目前正在等待批准。<br />\n<br />\n據一些了解審議情況的人士透露，審批的時間表沒有確定，該決定部分取決於中國疫苗在海外的獲批情況，這表明批準的時間在一定程度上受到了政治因素的影響。<br />\n<br />\n..."},{"pid":"d013589198eee785c8ddf62c1d704239e8fe9469","tid":2493343,"uid":26770,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T22:25:39.000Z","msg":"咪就係中國疲苗連鬼國班官都唔q信<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2021/04/12/chinese-officials-admit-that-chinas-vaccine-protection-is-low/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2021%2F04%2F12%2Fchinese-officials-admit-that-chinas-vaccine-protection-is-low%2F&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RPsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=fc686226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2021/04/12/chinese-officials-admit-that-chinas-vaccine-protection-is-low/</a><br />\n承認中國疫苗保護力低，中國官員：可能需要增加劑量<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係唔得就係唔得,打一桶都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa4fc80351f7409caa17f7ec89ae17a31477672","tid":2493343,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a263a95c1a694be6ee351624d1b87ea7a2245ca6","tid":2493343,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T22:23:08.000Z","msg":"中國計劃在7月前批准首款外國新冠疫苗<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.wsj.com/articles/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E5%9C%A87%E6%9C%88%E5%89%8D%E6%89%B9%E5%87%86%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%BE%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97-11618621214\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.wsj.com%2Farticles%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583%25E5%259C%25A87%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2589%258D%25E6%2589%25B9%25E5%2587%2586%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%258B%2597-11618621214&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RPsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=5828ac92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cn.wsj.com/articles/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E5%9C%A87%E6%9C%88%E5%89%8D%E6%89%B9%E5%87%86%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%BE%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97-11618621214</a><br />\n據知情人士透露，中國官員一直在仔細審視<span class=\"xx-large\">BioNTech</span>新冠疫苗的臨床試驗數據，目前國內科學家和外國商界要求中國將其疫苗名冊擴大到國產疫苗之外的壓力越來越大。<br />\nKeith Zhai / Liza Lin / Sha Hua<br />\n2021年4